text: The Liberal Party of Switzerland () or Swiss Liberal Party (; ; ) was a liberal political party in Switzerland. The Liberal Party was founded in 1913. On 1 January 2009, it merged with the Free Democratic Party (FDP/PRD) to become the FDP.The Liberals.
